altername_name: Ai Iijima Interactive Video Clip: Good Island Cafe
name: Ai Iijima: Good Island Cafe
overview: Ai Iijima: Good Island Cafe (飯島愛・グッドアイランドカフェ) is a Sega Saturn music video creation program developed and published by Inner Brain. Starring Japanese media personality Ai Iijima, it was released exclusively in Japan in September 1996.
